<h2>Speed Ordering</h2>
<p>To use Sonnax speed ordering, please fill in the part number and quantity fields for each item, then click the <strong>Add to Cart</strong> button. Speed and/or catalog ordered item lists will be combined on the same CART for you to review, update and submit as a single order to Sonnax.</p>

<p><strong class="note">Note</strong>: The Speed Order Form allows customers to quickly order Torque Converter, (<em>including High Performance Torque Converter</em>), Allison and Transmission Specialties&reg; parts. Please be aware that although orders can be entered on the Speed Order Form, <strong>these orders will only be filled for authorized customers</strong>.</p>
<!--<p>To use Speed Order Form: You can order from more than one product line on the same order; however, you can only select from one product line on a single form. Select one product line first, enter those part numbers and add them to your Cart, then return to this form and select another product line. All ordered items will be compiled in the Order Cart for your review prior to submitting the order.</p>-->
<form method="post" action="#" id="speed-order-form">
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Cart Contents</legend>
    <table class="speed-order" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Product Line</th>
          <th>Part Number</th>
          <th>Quantity</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tfoot></tfoot>
      <tbody>
    <% (1...5).each do |row| %>
    <tr id="line_item_<%= row %>">
      <td class="product-line">
        <label for="product_line_<%= row %>">Product Line</label>
        <select name="product_line" id="product_line_<%= row %>">
          <option value="2">Torque Converter &amp; HP Converter</option>
          	<option value="3">Transmission Specialties&reg;</option>
          	<option value="7">Allison&reg;</option>
        </select>
      </td>
      
      <td class="part-number">
        <label for="part_number_<%= row %>">Part Number</label>
        <input type="text" name="part_number[]" id="part_number_<%= row %>">
      </td>
      
      <td class="quantity">
        <label for="quantity_<%= row %>">Quantity</label>
        <input type="text" name="quantity[]" id="quantity_<%= row %>" size="2">
      </td>
    </tr>
    <% end %>
    </tbody>
    </table>
  </fieldset>
  <%= link_to 'Add another part...', '#', :class=> 'add-line-item add' %>
  
  <fieldset class="submit">
    <div><button type="submit" name="submit">Add to Cart</button></div>
  </fieldset>
</form>